You can start and stop the glusterd daemon manually, as required.

*To start glusterd manually*

* Enter the following command: +
 +
# /etc/init.d/glusterd start

*To stop glusterd manually*

* Enter the following command: +
 +
# /etc/init.d/glusterd stop

